sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Client
    participant A as API Server
    participant D as Database
    participant N as Notification Service

    U->>C: Create Task
    C->>A: POST /api/tasks
    Note over A,D: Validate task data
    A->>D: INSERT INTO tasks
    D-->>A: Task created
    A-->>C: Return task data
    C-->>U: Show created task

    Note over U,N: Async notification
    A->>N: Send notification
    N-->>A: Notification queued
    A-->>C: Task created response

    par Parallel notification
        N->>U: Email notification
    and
        N->>U: Push notification
    end
